# SYNAPSE — environment variables
#
# Web3Forms powers the contact form (free, no backend required).
# Get your free access key by entering your email at:
#   https://web3forms.com
#
# The key is public/safe to expose (it only allows sending to YOUR inbox).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables are inlined at build time, which is required for the
# static export (`next build` → `out/`).
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your key below.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your_access_key_here
